TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(USVETS_RACE='1','White', IIF(USVETS_RACE='2','Black or African american', IIF(USVETS_RACE='3','American Indian or Alaskan Native', IIF(USVETS_RACE='4','Asian', IIF(USVETS_RACE='5','Native Hawaiian or Pacific Islander', IIF(USVETS_RACE='6','Asian or Pacific Islander', IIF(USVETS_RACE='7','Other', IIF(USVETS_RACE='8','Two or more races', IIF(USVETS_RACE='Z','Multiple Race or Unknown','Multiple Race or Unknown')))))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_USVETS_RACE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(VADIR_RACE ='C','White', IIF(VADIR_RACE='M','Asian or Pacific Islander', IIF(VADIR_RACE='N','Black', IIF(VADIR_RACE='R','American Indian or Alaskan Native', IIF(VADIR_RACE='Z',' Multiple Race or Unknown', IIF(VADIR_RACE='X','Other','Multiple Race or Unknown'))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='White, not of Hispanic Origin','White, not of Hispanic Origin', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='Asian or Pacific Islander','Asian or Pacific Islander', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='Black, not of Hispanic Origin','Black, not of Hispanic Origin', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='American Indian or Alaskan Native','American Indian or Alaskan Native', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='Hispanic','Hispanic', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='Unknown','Multiple Race or Unknown','Multiple Race or Unknown'))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_RACE_SOURCE_CORP

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='White, not of Hispanic Origin','1', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='Asian or Pacific Islander','6', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='Black, not of Hispanic Origin','2', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='American Indian or Alaskan Native','3', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='Hispanic','H', IIF(CORP_RACE_TYPE='Unknown','Z','Z'))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='White','White', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Black or African American','Black or African American', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='American Indian or Alaska Native','American Indian or Alaska Native', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Asian','Asian', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Two or more races','Two or more races', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander','Native Hawaiian or Pacific Islander', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Unknown','Multiple Race or Unknown','Multiple Race or Unknown')))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_RACE_SOURCE_OEI

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='White','1', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Black or African American','2', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='American Indian or Alaska Native','3', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Asian','6', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Two or more races','Z', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Native Hawaiian or Other Pacific Islander','5', IIF(OEI_AGGREGATED_RACE='Unknown','Z','Z')))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'1','6','2','3'),v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR, IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'7') AND IN (USVETS_RACE,'1','2','3','4','5','6'),USVETS_RACE, IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'Z') AND IN (USVETS_RACE,'1','2','3','4','5','6'),USVETS_RACE, IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'7') AND IN(USVETS_RACE,'7'),v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR, IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'Z') AND IN(USVETS_RACE,'Z','8') ,v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR, IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'Z') AND IN(USVETS_RACE,'Z','8') AND v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP='H',v2_RACE_SOURCE_CORP, IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'Z') AND IN(USVETS_RACE,'7'),USVETS_RACE, IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'7') AND IN(USVETS_RACE,'Z','8'),v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR, 'Z' ))))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION='1','White', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION='2','Black or African american', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION='3','American Indian or Alaska Native', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION='4','Asian', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION='5','Native Hawaiian or Pacific Islander', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION='6','Asian or Pacific Islander', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION='7','Other', IIF(IN(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION,'8','Z'),'Multiple Race or Unknown Race','Multiple Race or Unknown Race'))))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v2_RACE_DESCRIPTION

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'1','6','2','3'),'V', IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'7') AND IN(v1_USVETS_RACE,'1','2','3','4','5','6'), 'U', IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'Z') AND IN(v1_USVETS_RACE,'1','2','3','4','5','6'), 'U', IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'7') AND IN(v1_USVETS_RACE,'7'),'V', IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'Z') AND IN(v1_USVETS_RACE,'Z','8'),'V', IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'Z') AND IN(v1_USVETS_RACE,'7'),'U', IIF(IN(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'7') AND IN(v1_USVETS_RACE,'Z','8'),'V','Z')))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: RACE_SOURCE_DESCRIPTION

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION=v1_USVETS_RACE,'COUV', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION=v1_USVETS_RACE,'COU', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'COV', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION=v1_USVETS_RACE,'CUV', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'CV', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI,'CO', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_USVETS_RACE,'CU', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR and v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION=v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP and v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_USVETS_RACE, 'C', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION=v1_USVETS_RACE,'OUV', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR,'OV', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_USVETS_RACE,'OU', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR and v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION!=v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP and v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION =v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_USVETS_RACE, 'O', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION= v1_USVETS_RACE,'UV', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR and v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION!=v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP and v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION =v1_USVETS_RACE, 'U', IIF(v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION = v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR and v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION!=v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP and v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI AND v1_RACE_DESCRIPTION !=v1_USVETS_RACE, 'V', IIF(v1_RACE_SOURCE_VADIR='Null' and v1_RACE_SOURCE_CORP='Null' and v1_RACE_SOURCE_OEI='Null' and v1_USVETS_RACE='Null','COUV'))))))))))))))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: RACE_MATCH_DESC
